    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 13 V&V 40 credibility factors assessed. Twelve of thirteen factors meet or exceed required level. One factor (Test conditions) achieved level 2 against a required level of 3; risk accepted given quasi-static loading regime and consistency with published F1717 precedent. All three QoIs satisfy quantitative acceptance criteria (E/uval < 1.96, percent difference < 10%). Overall credibility is sufficient to support regulatory submission for the non-cannulated 7.5 mm pedicle screw design.",
